{"html":"<div class="rd3-page">
    <header class="header" style="background-image: url('/apps/molgenis-viz/img/home-header.jpg');">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>MOLGENIS-RD3</h1>
            <p>The Rare Disease Database</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-filter" />
    </header>
    <div class="section bg-gray-050">
        <div class="section-content">
            <h2 id="section-intro-title">Overview</h2>
            <p><strong>MOLGENIS-RD3</strong> is a model and database that provides the structure for capturing and managing research metadata. This includes characteristics about individuals and samples that were collected from them, as well as metadata on the experiments performed and the results that were produced (e.g., files variant interpretations, etc.).</p>
            <p>There are a number of ways to get started. Click the "read more" link to learn about RD3 or start the submission process.</p>
            <a href="../pages/#/Submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit data</a>
            <a href="../pages/#/About" class="btn btn-link">Read more</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section bg-gray-000">
        <div class="section-content">
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-center">Please contact us if you have any questions about RD3 or need help with the submission process</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:support@molgenis.org">Email us</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>","css":".rd3-page {
    font-size: 14pt;
    font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; 
}

.rd3-page .header {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: 0 70%;
    height: 15em;
}

.rd3-page .header .content {
    width: 90%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 812px;
}

.rd3-page .header .content h1, 
.rd3-page .header .content p {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #f6f6f6;
}
.rd3-page .header .content h1 {
    font-size: 13pt;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.rd3-page .header .content p {
    font-size: 32pt;
    font-weight: 200;
}

.rd3-page .header .bg-filter {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: hsla(0,0%,0%, 0.40);
}

.rd3-page .section {
    box-sizing: content-box;
}

.rd3-page .section .section-content {
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 1024px;
    padding: 2em
}

.rd3-page .section .section-content h2 {
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: center;
}

.rd3-page .section .section-content p {
    line-height: 1.5;
}

.bg-gray-050 {
    background-color: #f6f6f6;
}

.bg-gray-000 {
    background-color: #ffffff;
}
